Name: athena-finger
Summary: The Athena version of the normal finger utility
Copyright: MIT and UCB
Group: Applications/Internet

Requires: athena-hesiod athena-zephyr

%description 
The finger command displays information about local and remote users
in a convenient format.  The Athena version contains improvements to
locate Athena users and knows about the Athena-specific user database
features.  
